<BaseLayout title="Zero Sorrys: Auditing the Goldbach Proof Chain — Perqed" activeNav="blog"
  description="An honest audit of our Lean 4 formalization found vacuous proofs, false theorems, and inflated counts. Here's how we fixed everything and decomposed the proof down to Rankin-Selberg positivity.">

