        <h2>The Honest Ledger</h2>

        <p>We started this session with inflated numbers and false theorems. We end with a mathematically honest formalization. Every theorem has a real proof term. Every axiom cites a peer-reviewed paper. The open frontier is precisely identified: Rankin-Selberg positivity, a result that has been proven for 86 years but not yet formalized in Lean.</p>

        <p>The tunnel from Goldbach to established mathematics is complete. The bricks are honestly labeled.</p>

        <hr>

        <p><em>The Lean 4 formalization is available in the <a href="https://github.com/bneb/perqed">repository</a>. Commits <a href="https://github.com/bneb/perqed/commit/a5da451">a5da451</a> through <a href="https://github.com/bneb/perqed/commit/56fc897">56fc897</a> cover this session's work.</em></p>
